  1. GI chart code definition

Map showing client connections

A map with manual mappings of client IPs to latitude and longitude connection to a hypothetical data center in Cape Town, South Africa.

  • Report category: Database activity

  • Required report headers:

    • Primary category: Server hostname
    • Secondary category: Client IP
    • Primary value: Count
In order to make practical use of this example, latitude and longitude mappings in the vega definition below should be replaced.
